dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Shows the Dnieper River in Ukraine, from Cherkasy to Ochakiv on the Black Sea. "Scala milliarium ad hunc tractum Boristhenis pertinens." Dutch text on verso with caption title: Moscovien; p. 18; signature R. Appears in Willem and Joan Blaeu's Toonneel des Aerdrycx, oft Nieuwe atlas, 1642 and other eds.
dct_spatial_sm: Russia. Russian Empire. Soviet Union. Former Soviet Republics
